Class NiMultipliedFilterTransactionMeasure

  • java.lang.Object

          • org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.schema.NiMultipliedFilterTransactionMeasure

  • public class NiMultipliedFilterTransactionMeasure
extends NiPredicateTransactionMeasure
    a measure defined as a filtered transaction multiplied by a number: for each cell, a configured callback decides a multiplier for it. In case the multiplier is null, the cell is dropped; else the result of multiplying the cell by the result is output
